# Accord Global Technology Solutions

> Engineering services company specialising in GNSS technology for aerospace, defence and space applications.

## What they do

Accord Global Technology Solutions is an engineering services company with expertise in Global Navigation Satellite System (GNSS) technology, providing engineering services across aerospace, automotive and digital technology. The business is headquartered in Bangalore, India, and supplies GNSS-based solutions for strategic and space programmes, including work for the Defence Research and Development Organisation and the Indian Space Research Organisation. It is an ADS member with a UK presence.

The company was acquired by Alten S.A. in June 2023 and subsequently renamed ALTEN Global Technologies Private Limited.

## Products and solutions

- **GNSS receivers** - GNSS-based receivers and solutions, including dual-frequency IRNSS/NavIC receivers, for aerospace, automotive, industrial and timing applications.
- **Embedded engineering services** - product engineering for avionics and real-time embedded systems.

